long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing WAXP Lite – your go-to solution for effortlessly extracting and exporting all your WhatsApp™ contacts straight to an Excel file! Perfect for seamless backups, this powerful tool lets you export contacts from your chatlist, groups, and labels into neatly organized Excel sheets, complete with names, numbers, countries, and more. Say goodbye to hassle and hello to streamlined backup solutions with WAXP Lite!

💰 Limited Free Trial
Keep in mind: while the free version exports all contacts, only 4 will be visible, with the rest hidden. Make sure the extension meets your needs during the trial period.
